          "startTime": 7.67582709
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9582.0127936,
          "startTime": 13.6833332062
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEのセクシー担当、鈴村優です\n肌に滴るお湯の一滴まで、綺麗に撮って下さいね",
      "startTime": 12.3122660403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "セクシー担当なんていつ決まったんだ？",
      "startTime": 17.1556687356,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4477.6647250000005,
          "startTime": 21.6333334606
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "もう、野暮なこと言わんといて\nそれより、ちゃんとうちを見てて下さい",
      "startTime": 24.0333334606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは恋人役なんやから\n瞬きするのも許さへんよ",
      "startTime": 30.4000003815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2787.231095599999,
          "startTime": 33.1872314771
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……。うちの入浴シーン、どうですか？\n大人っぽいうちの魅力にドキドキしてくれてますか？",
      "startTime": 38.4666650136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.332316100001,
          "startTime": 43.4999973297
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "初めてで不安もあったけど、ちゃんとやれてるんは\n{user}さんが見ててくれてるおかげや",
      "startTime": 47.033330663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちのことを、しっかり見ててくれる……\nしっかり……見られて……",
      "startTime": 54.1333291371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5899.9987284,
          "startTime": 60.0333278655
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……ん？　気のせいか）\n（優の顔がだんだん赤くなってきたような……）",
      "startTime": 60.6999945322,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.670226999993,
          "startTime": 67.0666647592
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "う、うぅ……ちょ、ちょっと、いつまで見てるん？\nそないにじろじろ見られたら……うぅ……",
      "startTime": 69.4333314258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "もう十分堪能したやろ？　これ以上見んといて\n{user}さんは外出とって下さい",
      "startTime": 77.9999950407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.201627
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.201627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……無事に撮影が終わって\nようやく肩の荷が下りたわ",
      "startTime": 87.233328374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8449601331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うちの入浴シーン、どうでした？\n途中までじろじろ見とったやろ",
      "startTime": 92.933328374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……改めて優は美人だと思ったよ\n色っぽいと言うより、綺麗だった",
      "startTime": 100.4235980844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4808104037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "え……\nそ、そないに真顔で言われると、さすがに照れるわ……",
      "startTime": 104.933328374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3999950407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お世辞じゃなく、本当に綺麗だと思ったんだ\n……だから、俺も覚悟を決めたよ",
      "startTime": 114.3999950407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "覚悟って……なんの話ですか？",
      "startTime": 117.0895176727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9024880408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "決まってるだろ。たとえ優のお母さんが\nどんな妨害をしてきても、俺は必ず優を守る！",
      "startTime": 123.9028414281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "土下座して、真心を込めて説明すれば\nお母さんも分かってくれるはずだ！",
      "startTime": 130.3051678685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0768193243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だから優は安心して\n自分のやりたいことをやってくれ！",
      "startTime": 134.733328374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n……ぷっ、ふふ、あははは！",
      "startTime": 140.1666617074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.0357340652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "何を言い出すかと思えば……お母さんが怒ってるって\n本気で信じてたん？　あれ冗談やで？",
      "startTime": 148.6333314258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "それどころか、やると決めたら、プロとしてしっかり\n仕事をしてこいって逆に発破をかけられたくらいや",
      "startTime": 156.896118052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.4482042152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……そ、そうだったのか……はぁ……\n優がお母さんと喧嘩していなくてホッとしたよ",
      "startTime": 166.9999970752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……うちの親よりも\n{user}さんの方がよっぽど過保護やね",
      "startTime": 173.6666637419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.1906766095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そこまで過保護なつもりはないんだが……",
      "startTime": 177.1906766095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてるん？　今日だってうちが緊張しないように\n朝からずっと気を使ってたやんか",
      "startTime": 185.8666637419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.0112888335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "うちより緊張してるのを見てたら\nからかいたくてたまらんかったわ",
      "startTime": 191.4999970752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.2405408858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの撮影でも、うちのタオルがはだけた時\n一人で大慌てして、慌てて目逸らして……",
      "startTime": 198.1877550601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "下はちゃんと水着着てるのに\nあんなに取り乱すなんて可愛いなぁ",
      "startTime": 204.6666637419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そのことは、もう勘弁してくれ……",
      "startTime": 207.9827857653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
