      "text": "はぁ……まいったわ……",
      "startTime": 223.298275121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ため息なんかついて、どうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 226.4916085402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "それが、昨日寮に帰ったら、発売されたばかりの\nうちの写真集を星見プロのみんなが回し読みしてたんよ",
      "startTime": 233.5999970752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "入浴シーンがセクシーだの色っぽいだの\n盛り上がってて、ほんまに恥ずかしかったわ",
      "startTime": 241.6508875847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、いい写真だと\nみんなが思ってくれたってことだから",
      "startTime": 248.1999970752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんよねぇ\n悪意がないから怒る訳にもいかんくて……",
      "startTime": 253.3999970752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも瑠依ちゃんは「優も新しいことに\n挑戦してるのね」って嬉しそうに言ってくれたわ",
      "startTime": 260.7333304086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんに褒められたんは嬉しいなぁ\nそれだけでも頑張って挑戦した甲斐があったわ",
      "startTime": 268.3347722663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "……本音を言うと\n初めての挑戦に少しだけ不安もあったんよ？",
      "startTime": 273.9039271423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu029.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんがずっとそばに\nいてくれたおかげで、楽しくお仕事が出来ました",
      "startTime": 281.6333304086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そこは本音だったんだな。急に出てけって言ったり\n優は冗談なのか分からないところがあるんだよなぁ",
      "startTime": 289.9255507103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu030.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、これからも、時々冗談言って茶化すかも\nしれへんけど、よろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 298.2351446299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。こちらこそ、これからもよろしく\n……一応聞くが、今の感謝の言葉は冗談じゃないよな？",
      "startTime": 307.2999909717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_03-yu031.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……ご想像にお任せします～",
      "startTime": 311.9954339823,
